                <h1>Black Sabbath Band Members: Legends of Heavy Metal</h1>
                <p>Black Sabbath, pioneers of heavy metal, originally featured iconic members: Ozzy Osbourne (vocals), Tony Iommi (guitar), Geezer Butler (bass), and Bill Ward (drums). Their innovative sound and dark themes revolutionized rock music. Each member contributed uniquely, creating a legacy that continues to influence today’s artists.</p>
